  }, {
    "indice" : 5,
    "estilo" : "Default",
    "original" : "{\\i1}I guess it's hard to judge how\\Nclose you can get to them...",
    "traduzido" : "{\\i1}Acho difícil julgar quanto\\Npode se aproximar deles...",
